# 🛍️ Product Recommendation System

## 📌 Overview
This project builds a recommendation system to suggest products based on user behavior and purchase history.

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib

---

## 🚀 Features
- Data preprocessing
- User-product interaction matrix
- Recommendation generation
- Model evaluation

---

